iterative approach (Ansatz):

      i	                   answer

      4                   	   4
      3	                  4 * 3 = 12
      2	                  12 * 2 = 24
      1                       24 * 2 = 1


recursive approach (Ansatz):

     function call	                    return value
                            	              
      factorial(1)                           1 (Basisfall)
      factorial(2)	                      2 * 1 = 2
      factorial(3)	                      3 * 2 = 6
      factorial(4)	                      4 * 6 = 24
